      "acceptanceCriteria": "Blood analog fluid must be characterized by viscometry at the test temperature; sample-to-sample variability must be quantified across at least three batches.",
      "rationale": "A single batch of glycerol-water analog was used for all experiments. No batch variability characterization was performed. Flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5."
